snippet.title: Sachin Tendulkar's Master 11 vs Akshay Kumar's Khiladi 11 | Highlights | ISPL | 6th March 2024
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony LIV Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/sonyliv
 
Click here to watch all highlights: https://bit.ly/3OVl9LM

Click here to watch more: https://www.sonyliv.com/sports/cricket-indian-street-premier-league-1700001390

Click here to subscribe now: https://bit.ly/3Q78rHU

Watch the highlights of the inaugural match between Sachin Tendulkar's Master 11 and Akshay Kumar's Khiladi 11 in the Indian Street Premier League 2024. Sachin Tendulkar's Master 11 scored 94 runs in 10 overs and lost 7 wickets in the process. Sachin was the top scorer with 30 runs. Akshay Kumar's Khiladi 11 then put up a strong performance during the chase but lost the match by 5 runs in the end. 

Master 11: Sachin Tendulkar, Amir, Suresh Raina, Yusuf Pathan, Stuart Binny, Rishabh Chavan, Munaf Patel, Ram Charan, Kunal Khemmu, Samir Kochhar, Elvish Yadav.

Khiladi 11: Akshay Kumar, Suriya, Irfan Pathan, Robin Uthappa, Praveen Kumar, Naman Ojha, Gaurav Taneja, Prateik Babbar, Sukhwinder Singh, Munawar Farooqui, Riyaz Ali.

snippet.title: Srinagar Ke Veer vs Majhi Mumbai | Highlights | ISPL | 6th March 2024
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony LIV Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/sonyliv
 
Click here to watch all highlights: https://bit.ly/3OVl9LM

Click here to watch more: https://www.sonyliv.com/sports/cricket-indian-street-premier-league-1700001390

Click here to subscribe now: https://bit.ly/3Q78rHU

Majhi Mumbai scored a superb total of 140 runs for the loss of 7 wickets in their 10 overs against Srinagar Ke Veer. Srinagar Ke Veer could not manage to chase down the big total and ended up with just 103 runs and lost 7 wickets in the process. Majhi Mumbai won by 37 runs in the end.

snippet.title: GOAT BLOOD FRY | Traditional Goat Blood Recipe Cooking In Village | Goat Blood Gravy with Intestine
snippet.description:
Today in our village, We cook our village's traditional goat blood recipe by making blood gravy and blood fry. We call this recipe as "Raththa Koottu" and "Raththa Poriyal". We add some goat internal parts to goat blood gravy, such as the liver, lungs, and intestine.

Finally, we enjoy the food with our favourite muttun curry! The taste is delicious!

*About* 
------------

                Police officer Virat Chavan ne diya vaada apne marte hue junior ko ke rakhenge woh khayal unki beti, Sai ka. Virat aur Sai bandh gaye anchaahe shaadi ke bandhan mai. Virat ka dil tha Patralekha ke paas jiski shaadi hojati hai kisi aur se. Virat ne vaada kiya Pakhi se ke woh uski jagah kabhi kisi aur ko nahi dega. 
                Virat ne bhale nahi diya Sai ko ek pati ka pyaar par unke rishtey mai izzat hamesha thi. Waqt ke saath saath, Virat ne dekha Sai ka accha roop aur hogaya ussey Sai se pyaar. Yeh kahani hai Virat, Sai aur Patralekha ke pyaar ki.

How to Make Upvasacha Dosa Recipe / Upvasachi Amboli-
 ‚Ä¢ In a mixing bowl take sama rice, wash the rice well and soak it for 4-5 hours.
 ‚Ä¢ Wash Sago / sabudana and soak for 4-5 hours.
 ‚Ä¢ After 4-5 hours, in a grinding jar add soaked sama rice and grind well and pour the batter to a large mixing bowl.
 ‚Ä¢ Grind the soaked sago too and pour the mixture into the same rice batter.
 ‚Ä¢ Now into the grinding jar take fresh coconut & Rajgira puffs and require water and grind & pout the mixture to the sama rice batter.
 ‚Ä¢ Mix everything well and let it sit for overnight or 10-12 hours for fermentation.
 ‚Ä¢ After fermentation, add salt and mix well.
 ‚Ä¢ To make Amboli or Dosa, Neer Dosa, heat up dosa pan, apply oil and pour dosa batter and spread.
 ‚Ä¢ Cook¬† on medium heat for a minute or two and , when you see dosa edges are drying, apply some oil or ghee, and take it out.¬†
 ‚Ä¢ Our Upvasacha Dosa / Upvasachi Amboli is ready to serve
.¬†

How to Make Upvasacha Dosa Recipe / Upvasachi Amboli-
 ‚Ä¢ In a mixing bowl take sama rice, wash the rice well and soak it for 4-5 hours.
 ‚Ä¢ Wash Sago / sabudana and soak for 4-5 hours.
 ‚Ä¢ After 4-5 hours, in a grinding jar add soaked sama rice and grind well and pour the batter to a large mixing bowl.
 ‚Ä¢ Grind the soaked sago too and pour the mixture into the same rice batter.
 ‚Ä¢ Now into the grinding jar take fresh coconut & Rajgira puffs and require water and grind & pout the mixture to the sama rice batter.
 ‚Ä¢ Mix everything well and let it sit for overnight or 10-12 hours for fermentation.
 ‚Ä¢ After fermentation, add salt and mix well.
 ‚Ä¢ To make Amboli or Dosa, Neer Dosa, heat up dosa pan, apply oil and pour dosa batter and spread.
 ‚Ä¢ Cook¬† on medium heat for a minute or two and , when you see dosa edges are drying, apply some oil or ghee, and take it out.¬†
 ‚Ä¢ Our Upvasacha Dosa / Upvasachi Amboli is ready to serve
.¬†

Episode 4025: Birthday Ke Din Gayab
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide posts a birthday message for Popatlal on the society board. Concerned about Popatlal's unavailability, everyone attempts to reach him without success and turns to Abdul for information. Sodhi and Bhide, eager to celebrate, make party plans, unaware that Champaklal overhears their conversation.

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Mrs. Nita Ambani's Performance to Vishwambhari Stuti For Anant & Radhika's Prewedding Celebration
snippet.description:
Celebrating tradition and invoking the divine, Mrs. Nita Ambani presents a stirring performance to the Vishwambhari Stuti, a sacred hymn dedicated to Maa Ambe, the embodiment of power and strength. She has been hearing this hymn since her childhood during every Navratri. Tonight, as she performs with grace and devotion, she seeks Maa Ambe's blessings for Anant and Radhika's journey of togetherness. She also dedicates her performance to her granddaughters, Aadiya Shakti and Veda, and to all young girls, who are a symbol of feminine energy. 

Credits:
Director & Director of Choreography: Vaibhavi Merchant.
Creative Director: Shruti Merchant. 
Music Directors/Composers: Ajay-Atul
Singer: Shreya Ghoshal
Director of Photography: Anil Mehta 
Production Design: Amrita Mahal
Mrs. Nita Ambani's Costume: Manish Malhotra
Dancers' Costume: Ashley Rebello

#AnantRadhika
#ARPreWeddingCelebrations #NitaMukeshAmbaniCulturalCentre
#SwadeshOnline

Episode 4024: Akele Mein Birthday
--------------------------------------------------------
The Tapu Sena makes a heartfelt visit to Popatlal's house to extend their wishes, but Popatlal, feigning absence, switches off his phone. Undeterred, he celebrates alone at home. Later, as conversations about Popatlal's marriage unfold, he inadvertently overhears the discussions, adding a poignant touch to the solitude surrounding him.

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Khaie Episode 23 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Sparx Smartphones - Faysal Quraishi - Durefishan Saleem - 6th March 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Khaie Digitally Presented by Sparx Smartphones #shinewithsparx
Get Ready to be Enthralled by 'Khaie' - Brought to You by Geo TV with the Cutting-Edge Innovation of Sparx Smartphone as the Exclusive Digital Presenting Partner. A Spectacular Journey Awaits

The story is a revenge saga that unfolds against the backdrop of the ancient tradition of Khaie, where the male members of an enemy's family are eliminated to stop the continuation of their lineage.  At the center of this age-old vendetta are Darwesh Khan, Duraab Khan, and his son Channar Khan, with Zamdaa, the daughter of Darwesh, bearing the heaviest consequences.  
Darwesh Khan is haunted by his father's murder at the hands of Duraab Khan. Seeking a peaceful life, Darwesh aims to broker a truce to end generational enmity. However, suspicions arise, and Duraab Khan and his son Channar Khan doubt Darwesh's intentions for peace.
Despite the genuine efforts of Darwesh, a kind-hearted man with a message for peace, a tragic turn of events unfolds during a celebration at Darwesh's home, causing immense suffering for Zamdaa and her family.
Will Zamdaa bow down in front of her enemies? If not, then will Zamdaa be able to take revenge on her family culprits? Will Zamdaa find allies in her journey, or will she face her enemies alone?

Written By: Saqlain Abbas
Directed By: Syed Wajahat Hussain
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.title: Thankamani | Trailer | Dileep | Ratheesh Reghunandan | Super Good Films | Saina Music | Iffaar Media
snippet.description:
Thankamani is an upcoming Indian Malayalam-language crime thriller film written and directed by Ratheesh Reghunandan and Produced by R B Choudhry under the banner of Super good films in association with Iffaar Media Raaffi Mathirra. The film stars Dileep and is based on a real-life incident that occurred in Thankamany in October 1986. Thankamani Music Rights has been acquired by Saina Music.

Written & Directed by Ratheesh Reghunandan
Produced by  RB Choudary , Raaffi Mathirra
D.O.P Manoj Pillai
Editor Shyam Sasidharan
Music William Francis
Executive Producer Sujit J Nair

Production Controller Mohan (Amritha)
Project Head Sumith B P
Asso. Directors Abhijith PR, Jophin Vargheese

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Ghaata Episode 61 [Eng Sub] - Adeel Chaudhry - Momina Iqbal - Mirza Zain Baig - 6th March 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Hamza and Rania are deeply in love, a fact known to the entire family. Yet, unbeknownst to them, their cousins Danish and Sana secretly harbor affection for the couple.
A tragic event turns Rania‚Äôs life upside down and has major consequences for her relationship with Hamza. Danish and Sana, motivated by their hidden malice, use the event to their advantage.
As the aftermath unfolds, the four cousins experience the hardships of love, betrayal, and suffering. Boundaries are crossed, and each of them battles personal demons in their pursuit of love.
Will Rania and Hamza manage to be together? Can Rania overcome the haunting consequences of the event, or will it define her life? Will Hamza stand by Rania during the most testing time of her life? And will Danish and Sana confess their feelings to Rania and Hamza, respectively?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation

snippet.title: ‡¥™‡µÅ‡¥§‡¥ø‡¥Ø ‡¥µ‡µÄ‡¥ü‡µç‡¥ü‡¥ø‡¥≤‡µÜ ‡¥ß‡µç‡¥µ‡¥®‡¥ø ‡¥Æ‡µã‡µæ‡¥ü‡µÜ ‡¥µ‡¥ø‡¥∂‡µá‡¥∑‡¥ô‡µç‡¥ô‡µæ | Dwani's Formula Milk Experience | MRIDVA
snippet.description:
üåü Welcome to Mridva Vlogs! üåü
In today's heartwarming episode, we delve deep into our baby's night time routine, highlighting the pivotal role that Aptamil plays in ensuring our little one gets the best start in life. üçº As new parents, finding the perfect formula milk was a journey filled with learning and love. Our chosen infant formula milk has been a cornerstone in our nightly routine, providing not just nourishment but peace of mind.
üë∂ Why Aptamil Gold Stage 1? Well, as we navigated the challenges of colic in infants and the quest for the best formula milk, it stood out for its commitment to infant nutrition and infant immunity. The transition to formula milk for newborns was made smoother with its advanced formulation, designed to meet the nutritional needs of infants in the most wholesome way possible.
In tonight's vlog, we not only share our soothing bedtime ritual but also how Formula Milk powder, specifically Aptamil Gold Stage 1, seamlessly integrates into our routine. This lactose-free formula milk (a blessing for sensitive little tummies) and infant formula powder have supported our baby's growth and development beautifully, echoing the principles of nutrition pediatrics.
üìñ From dimming the lights to wrapping up in snuggly blankets and embarking on fairy-tale adventures before bedtime, every step is a step towards growth and bonding. This formula milk  has been with us every step of the way, ensuring our baby's dietary needs are met with the highest standard of care.
üí° Whether you're a new parent grappling with the vast world of formula milk or seeking insights on infant nutrition, join us as we share our personal experiences with it. It's more than just a feeding solution; it's our trust in a brand that values the health and happiness of our most precious ones.
Remember, every child's needs are unique, and it's essential to consult with a healthcare provider to choose the best infant formula milk for your baby.
üëâ Don't forget to LIKE, SHARE, and SUBSCRIBE for more insights into our family's journey and tips on parenting, nutrition, and well-being. Drop your questions and experiences in the comments below‚Äîwe love hearing from you!

snippet.title: #Exclusive | Anant Ambani And Rahul Kanwal Take a Tour of Vantara Kingdom Elephant Kitchen
snippet.description:
#anantambani #rahulkanwal #anantambaniengagement #mukeshambani #vantara #RadhikaMerchant #NitaAmbani 
Step into the fascinating world of Vantara Kingdom's Elephant Kitchen with Rahul Kanwal, Executive Director of Business Today, and Anant Ambani, Director of Reliance Industries Limited, in a special edition of 'Jab We Met'. Embark on an exclusive tour as Anant Ambani and Rahul Kanwal explore the intricacies of the Elephant Kitchen, where the majestic residents of Vantara Kingdom are nourished. Witness firsthand as Rahul Kanwal delves into the unique culinary offerings for the elephants, discovering surprising treats that are not only savored by these gentle giants but also enjoyed by humans. From tasting delectable ladoos to refreshing watermelon juice, indulging in wholesome khichdi, and savoring popcorn treats meant for the elephants, Rahul Kanwal immerses himself in the culinary delights of Vantara Kingdom's Elephant Kitchen. Experience the joy of this extraordinary encounter as Anant Ambani and Rahul Kanwal unravel the secrets of this special sanctuary.

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS! SUPERB FODEN BRACE INSPIRES CITY TO DERBY TRIUMPH | Man City 3-1 Man United
snippet.description:
Phil Foden scored two stunning goals as City recovered from a goal down to beat Manchester United 3-1.

City had fallen behind to a thunderous Marcus Rashford goal on eight minutes - against the run of play - and spent the next 50 minutes or so trying to find a way past a resolute United back-line.

But Foden levelled on 56 minutes with a screamer into the top corner from 20 yards, then scored a delightful second ten minutes from the end of normal time.

Erling Haaland wrapped up victory with a clinical finish following excellent work by Rodrigo to make it 3-1 in added time as the Blues moved within a point of leaders Liverpool.

snippet.title: Gaami Trailer | Vishwak Sen | Chandini Chowdary | Vidyadhar Kagita | UV Creations
snippet.description:
Gaami Trailer On UV Creations.

#Gaami chronicles the adventurous journey of Shankar- a wounded, reluctant and reclusive Aghora on his quest to find the cure for his very rare condition- ‚Äòan inability to experience any human touch‚Äô.  But this adventure for cure would be fulfilled, only when he can confront and conquer his destiny that becomes intertwined with two other characters.
